data.description: Welcome to this exquisite home that offers a plethora of features and upgrades! As you step inside, check out the crown molding and pillar adorned with decorative facia. Storm doors with screens have been installed on both the front and back door, enhancing energy efficiency and allowing privacy. The home offers an array of desirable amenities. The wet bar area is equipped with a wine refrigerator, cabinets, a triple reverse osmosis system, and an ice maker. The kitchen showcases beautiful granite countertops, hand-painted tiles inspired by Van Gogh, adding a touch of artistic charm. The media center has a 72" fireplace with surround sound. The office room has wainscoting. The house is equipped with a smart home system, allowing you to control various functions both in the front and back of the house from a centralized network. All appliances are smart. Convenient features such as a hands-free dryer and a dog watering station, plumbed inside. The garage is a car enthusiast's dream, featuring epoxy flooring, ample lighting, and cabinets for storage. The third garage bay has been transformed into a full workshop catering to your DIY projects and hobbies. The front yard boasts elegant trees and a variety of fruit trees, including lemon, lime, Rainer cherry trees, apple pear, and Asian pear, creating a delightful atmosphere. The backyard is meticulously landscaped, featuring trees, lush grass, a gondola, and two sheds. A commercial flagpole proudly stands, adding a touch of distinction. Outside, a pergola with a firepit on a concrete pad beckons you to relax and unwind. The jacuzzi pad, wired for a jacuzzi, is currently occupied by a greenhouse, offering versatility and potential for your personal preferences. This home offers a seamless flow from the front to the back with a concrete path on the side yard, ensuring easy access. Enjoy the comfort of 20x20 Sun Setter shades with electric operation, reducing the temperature inside by approximately 10 degrees during hot summer days. Embrace sustainable living with owned solar panels and a backup battery, ensuring a reliable and eco-friendly power source. There is a LEVEL 2 electric car charger in garage, charges 6 times faster than level 1. Don't miss the opportunity to own this meticulously upgraded and thoughtfully designed home. Its exceptional features and attention to detail make it a truly remarkable residence.
